        {
            "title": "深水埗汝州街天台火警　一名女子不適",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"汝州街發生火警。fb：深水埗街坊會\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/0f66f4f3a9ab825494ddecf240ddbd2f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250220/_2025022008402922157.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">汝州街發生火警。fb：深水埗街坊會</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（20日）晨7時許，深水埗汝州街251號東興大廈的天台起火，濃煙席捲半空，消防員接報到場升起雲梯灌救，一名女子表示不適，登上救護車接受治理。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091937/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"汝州街發生火警。fb：深水埗街坊會\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0ed29810084e08c60d2d3b7146a5ef31/2025-02/888_15.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        汝州街發生火警。fb：深水埗街坊會\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
